<!DOCTYPE subsection SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<subsection title="Keyboard Shortcuts">
  <p>Mingle's new WYSIWYG editor supports the following keyboard shortcuts</p>
    <bullets>
      <bullets>
        <bullets>
          <item>Bold: <strong>CTRL + B</strong></item>
          <item>Underline: <strong>CTRL + U</strong></item>
          <item>Italic: <strong>CTRL + I</strong></item>
          <item>Hyperlink: <strong>CTRL + K</strong></item>
          <item>Highlight URL: <strong>CTRL + L</strong></item>
          <item>Number list: <strong>CTRL + SHIFT + 7</strong></item>
          <item>Bullet list: <strong>CTRL + SHIFT + 8</strong></item>
        </bullets>
      </bullets>
    </bullets>
    <p>For a full list of accessibility instructions and keyboard shortcuts press <strong>ALT + 0</strong>.</p>
</subsection>
